										Specify 4BR3200	$8.00

For non-gate-array (three-ROM) Model 4 and Model III systems.


Model 4 U4 PAL - Video clock generator - 8075268	
										Specify 4PU4000	$5.00

For non-gate-array Model 4 systems.


Model 4 U59 PAL - ROM/Video/Keyboard address decoder - 8075368		
										Specify 4PU5900	$5.00

For non-gate-array Model 4 systems.



TRSDOS 06.02.01 System Disk
										Specify 4GR6201	$10.00

.fi
The last version of TRSDOS 6.x sold under the Tandy name.  It
does not accept dates after 1987, but patches are available to extend
the range of the date in a way similar to what LS-DOS 6.3.x does.
Printed documentation is not included.
We will replace the MODELA/III file on these disks with our latest version
unless you request otherwise.


.nf
LS-DOS 06.03.01	System Disk
										Specify 4GR6301	$20.00

.fi
Tandy obtained rights to LS-DOS from Logical Systems and then Misosys for
sale of LS-DOS 6.3 to Tandy customers via the Tandy special order catalog.
There is no manual and we have a very limited quantity of these disks.
These disks do not contain the last patch-level released by MISOSYS, but you
can apply the patches yourself.  We will replace the MODELA/III file on these
disks with our latest version unless you request otherwise.   


.nf
TRSDOS 01.03.02 System Disk
										Specify 4GR1302	$5.00

.fi
The last version of Model III TRSDOS 1.x widely distributed by Tandy.  We
will replace the MODELA/III file with the latest version unless you request
otherwise.
.nf


----------------------------------------------------------------------------

MODELA/III Data Diskette
										Specify 4PD3000	$1.00

.fi
This is the latest version of the MODELA/III, straight from the original
author.  It allows the Model 4P user to take advantage of most of the
Model III-mode features of our XROM and XDROM products.  The MODELA/III
file is for systems with US keyboards.  It is not usable with German
or French systems.  This disk is in the TRSDOS 1.3.x format.

This item will be included at no charge (on request) with a purchase of
$10 or more.
.nf


